n<br />\n由一開始家姐帶仔番屋企<br />\n到到描述隻臭拖鞋既化學反應<br />\n再轉到樓豬同醫生耐人尋味既關係<br />\n最後帶出樓豬有輕度思覺失調<br />\n<br />\n成篇文睇到我停唔到<br />\n食緊飯睇食左半粒鐘都冇扒過一啖飯<br />\n隔離台見到我一路睇一路笑到震曬<br />\n細細話條友係咪痴撚左線<br />\n以為我聽唔到<br />\n<br />\n我輕輕啜一啖凍檸茶<br />\n令一令頭<br />\n我從篇文已經領會到樓豬既心路歷程<br />\n你呢d世人撚會明白<br />\n我同樓豬之間既精神交流"},{"pid":"bc131351588f5e34c94b4fb0a8f615ca24f4c776","tid":809180,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5d5440077c6dfc78601420dd862af911dc38b8","tid":809180,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57d55c3740ed07fb5058138f1e5fe9a16e1001e0","tid":809180,"uid":25900,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"不過第一次見 d reply話childon仔高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知原來係高登原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"又炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd05a87513593394cbcdc8319115fb8dc7a3f0c","tid":809180,"uid":70943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"抄登果然係抄登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd35d0caebe1beed2f506f1cabf5f768979c8f8","tid":809180,"uid":205806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm